#define R(p,a,t) mix(a*dot(p,a),p,cos(t))+sin(t)*cross(p,a)
#define H(h) (cos((h)*6.3+vec3(0,23,21))*.5+.5)

void mainImage(out vec4 O, vec2 C)
{
    vec3 p,r=iResolution,c=vec3(0),
    d=normalize(vec3((C-.5*r.xy)/r.y,1));
    float i=0.,s,e,g=0.,t=iTime;
	for(;i++<90.;){
        p=g*d;
        p.z+=t;
        p=R(p,vec3(.577),clamp(sin(t*.5)*3.,-1.,1.)*.2+.1);
	    p=abs(p)-1.;
	    p=p.x<p.y?p.zxy:p.zyx;
	    p=asin(sin(p));
	    p=abs(p)-1.5;
	    s=2.;
	    p-=vec3(2,-3,.5);
	    for(int i=0;i<8;i++){
	        p=abs(p);
	        p=p.x<p.y?p.zxy:p.zyx;
	        s*=e=2.3/clamp(dot(p,p),.2,1.1);
	        p=abs(p)*e-vec3(.1,3,6.);
	    }
	    g+=e=abs(length(p-clamp(p,-8.,8.))-8.)/s+1e-5;
	    c+=vec3(.2,1,.9)*.018/exp(i*i*e);
	}
	c*=c*c;

    O=vec4(c,1);
}
